data.name: DescTitle.Text
data.value: Welcome to the Jump King RPC!

data.name: descText.Text
data.value: This is a program that collects information from the game 'Jump King' and let you have a Discord Rich Presence client. This application does not other than scan the Jump King executive file memory used and parse information such as: the location the player is in, the time elapsed from the start, the number of sessions and much more. Check out more information .
